# Daily Trips API Tests

### Test Authentication (Get Token First)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@example.com",
    "password": "password"
}

### Get All Daily Trips
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/daily-trips
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Vehicles for Dropdown
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/daily-trips-vehicles
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### Create New Daily Trip
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/daily-trips
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "month_year": "September 2025",
    "department": "Sales",
